Node:	tracker (Motion to follow object around robot)
Services:
	Client: servo_srv
Topics:
	Subscriber: tpc_track (size=5)
Input:
	None
Config:
	(var) last_position: maintains the current position of the servo
	(global const) _SERVO_SPEED_: 50 rpm
	(global const) _SERVO_POS_CHANGE_: 20 degrees
Output:
	None
Steps:
	Initialization: Begin subscribing to tpc_tracker
	1. 	Find the minimum distance measured from each sensor
		(a) if minimum is not center, then:
			(i) send request to servo_srv to move toward sensor with minimum measurement
		(b) else do nothing
